snippet.title: Bayonetta 3 – Nintendo Direct 9.13.22 – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
This one is for the angels in the audience! Join Bayonetta for a devilishly good time in this hair-raising, demon-summoning adventure.

Bayonetta 3 releases on Nintendo Switch 10/28. 
Pre-order today!
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/bayonetta-3-switch/
